{"id": 4622, "date": "2018-09-29T05:00:18", "date_gmt": "2018-09-29T12:00:18", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=4622"}, "modified": "2021-12-13T05:40:08", "modified_gmt": "2021-12-13T13:40:08", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-gary-u-s-bonds-and-bruce-springsteen-school-is-out", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/09/29/meeting-across-the-river-gary-u-s-bonds-and-bruce-springsteen-school-is-out/", "title": {"rendered": "Meeting Across the River: Gary U.S. Bonds and Bruce Springsteen, School Is Out"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>This one&#8217;s for the completists (like me).</p>\n<p>&#8220;School Is Out&#8221; was Gary U.S. Bonds follow-up to his smash hit (and frequent Springsteen encore) &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/08/21/cover-me-quarter-to-three/\">Quarter to Three</a>.&#8221;</p>\n<p>Released in 1961, &#8220;School Is Out&#8221; is certainly cut from the same cloth as its predecessor, opening with the same count-in, the same hand-clap syncopation, and the same use of background hoots and whistles.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Gary US Bonds  - School Is Out\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yUVAxBZojWQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>It was perhaps too similar to match the chart performance of &#8220;Quarter to Three&#8221; but close enough to get some lift from it, peaking at #5 in the US.</p>\n<p>Bruce has covered it once only&#8211;with Gary himself, on stage at the Old Waldorf in San Francisco, on a River Tour break back in June of 1981.</p>\n<p>The sound quality is terrible, but it&#8217;s the only document we have of Bruce performing this early rock hit. Give it a listen below (for as long as you can).</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Gary US Bonds cover :  School is out\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k_hSYvYqZ-Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>School Is Out</strong><strong><br />\nFirst performed:</strong>\u00a0June 15, 1981 (San Francisco, CA)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:\u00a0</strong>June 15, 1981 (San Francisco, CA)</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce&#8217;s one-and-only performance of &#8220;School Is Out&#8221; was with its original recording artist back in 1981.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 4917, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [4, 5], "tags": [80, 1714], "class_list": ["post-4622", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-cover-me", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-gary-u-s-bonds", "tag-school-is-out"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/schoolisout.jpg?fit=300%2C300&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-1cy", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 15412, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/01/17/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-gary-u-s-bonds-soul-deep/", "url_meta": {"origin": 4622, "position": 0}, "title": "MatR: Bruce Springsteen and Gary U.S. Bonds: Soul Deep", "author": "Ken", "date": "January 17, 2020", "format": false, "excerpt": "Did he or didn't he? Bruce and Gary U.S. Bonds played \"Soul Deep\" on stage together in 2003, but the jury's out on whether that was really Bruce's first time singing the 1969 blue-eyed soul classic with Gary.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/the-box-tops-soul-deep-bell-8.jpg?fit=700%2C705&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/the-box-tops-soul-deep-bell-8.jpg?fit=700%2C705&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/the-box-tops-soul-deep-bell-8.jpg?fit=700%2C705&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/the-box-tops-soul-deep-bell-8.jpg?fit=700%2C705&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 11079, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/07/01/matr-gary-u-s-bonds-and-bruce-springsteen-cant-teach-an-old-dog-new-tricks/", "url_meta": {"origin": 4622, "position": 1}, "title": "MatR: Gary U.S. Bonds and Bruce Springsteen, Can&#8217;t Teach an Old Dog New Tricks", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 1, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "Twenty-plus years after their last collaboration, Bruce joins Gary U.S. Bonds in the studio once more for \"Can't Teach an Old Dog New Tricks.\"", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Meeting Across the River&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Meeting Across the River", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/meeting-across-the-river/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/backin20.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/backin20.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/backin20.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 32111, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/01/20/matr-rotd-gary-u-s-bonds-and-bruce-springsteen-loves-on-the-line/", "url_meta": {"origin": 4622, "position": 2}, "title": "MatR/RotD: Gary U.S. Bonds and Bruce Springsteen: Love&#8217;s on the Line", "author": "Ken", "date": "January 20, 2022", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce's original River-era composition, a stellar E Street Band performance and Gary's passionate vocals make for a standout track on an album full of them.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ontheline.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ontheline.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ontheline.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ontheline.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ontheline.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 3401, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/07/27/cover-me-gary-u-s-bonds-your-love/", "url_meta": {"origin": 4622, "position": 3}, "title": "RotD/Cover Me, Gary U.S. Bonds: Your Love", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 27, 2018", "format": false, "excerpt": "One of many great songs Bruce gave away, \"Your Love\" is the missing link in a story that begins with \"Little White Lies\" and ends with \"My Love Will Not Let You Down.\"", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/dedication.jpg?fit=597%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/dedication.jpg?fit=597%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/dedication.jpg?fit=597%2C600&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 4184, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/09/06/rotd-matr-cover-me-gary-u-s-bonds-bruce-springsteen-the-e-street-band-this-little-girl/", "url_meta": {"origin": 4622, "position": 4}, "title": "ROTD/MatR/Cover Me, Gary U.S. Bonds, Bruce Springsteen &#038; The E Street Band, This Little Girl", "author": "Ken", "date": "September 6, 2018", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce penned \"This Little Girl\" for Gary U.S. Bonds' comeback album, and it worked--providing Bonds with a Top 40 (and almost a Top 10) hit, powered by the E Street Band and Bruce's lyrics, music, and backing vocals.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/thislittlegirl_sin-us-07i-e1536016722588.jpg?fit=500%2C481&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200}, "classes": []}, {"id": 26452, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/04/18/rotd-matr-gary-u-s-bonds-bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-out-of-work/", "url_meta": {"origin": 4622, "position": 5}, "title": "RotD/MatR: Gary U.S. Bonds, Bruce Springsteen and the E Street Band: Out of Work", "author": "Ken", "date": "April 18, 2021", "format": false, "excerpt": "As timely today as it was in the summer of '82, Bruce's slyly comedic \"Out of Work\" was a Top Forty hit for Gary U.S. Bonds.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/gary-us-bonds-out-of-work-1982-4.jpg?fit=700%2C697&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/gary-us-bonds-out-of-work-1982-4.jpg?fit=700%2C697&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/gary-us-bonds-out-of-work-1982-4.jpg?fit=700%2C697&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/gary-us-bonds-out-of-work-1982-4.jpg?fit=700%2C697&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}], "_links": {"self": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/4622", "targetHints": {"allow": ["GET"]}}], "collection": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}], "about": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}], "author": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/users/1"}], "replies": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=4622